  "1061100": {
    "name": "猎人竞技场：传奇",
    "steam_appid": 1061100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/ef95d831da7099fad7ce7353d66e9d58.avif?t=1713182577\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >前言</h2></strong><br>远古亚洲时期，一股未知力量释放出了妖怪，往昔的和平随之化为泡影。<br>世界各地的猎人们察觉到了巨大的危机，于是聚集于此，只为结束混沌之境。<br>然而，猎人们很快查出是他们中的一人破除了封印，释放了妖怪。<br>由于不能相信任何人，猎人们必须击败妖怪，与彼此兵戎相见。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >把握时机与制定决策的艺术</h2></strong><br>猎人竞技场的战斗系统与体术电影中的打斗动作相似。整个游戏的核心在于空中连击敌军，杀伐决断截击对手，扭转战局<br><br>有许多种方式绕开敌军，在战局中处于优势。<br>选择恰当时间使用瞬移可以把战斗的节奏掌握在自己手中，或者使用体术中和敌军防御。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/68757a784ced1cf1854758060437f347.poster.avif?t=1713182577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/68757a784ced1cf1854758060437f347.webm?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/68757a784ced1cf1854758060437f347.mp4?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>然而，使用这些技能也总是存在着很大的风险。遭遇截击时，使用体术会使你陷入昏迷状态，并且瞬移避敌可能会使你遭遇敌军炮火。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/a6f448570853e18253fec291d3e2f420.poster.avif?t=1713182577\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/a6f448570853e18253fec291d3e2f420.webm?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/a6f448570853e18253fec291d3e2f420.mp4?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >来自PvP和PvE的威胁</h2></strong><br>猎人竞技场设计提供一种独一无二的大逃杀体验。据说，你会在游戏中同时遇见PvP 和 PvE元素。对于PvE的粉丝而言，你可以探索地牢，杀死妖怪boss抢夺稀有战利品，变得更强大。对于PvP快节奏战斗的粉丝来说，你可以猎杀其他猎人，提升等级，证明自己是顶级猎手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/9ff7c4cd29942b916b8435ec5cd769d5.poster.avif?t=1713182577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/9ff7c4cd29942b916b8435ec5cd769d5.webm?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/9ff7c4cd29942b916b8435ec5cd769d5.mp4?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在“三人激战”模式中，你可以和朋友或其他玩家组团，以三人组队的形式实现胜利。你会以三人组队的形式进入竞技场来展现你的团队协作或者分散侦查敌情。“三人激战”模式归结起来就是制定战略和小组合作。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/93b6d6ab2d6f8cb8d583fc2762ec8e0d.poster.avif?t=1713182577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/93b6d6ab2d6f8cb8d583fc2762ec8e0d.webm?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/93b6d6ab2d6f8cb8d583fc2762ec8e0d.mp4?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在猎人竞技场中，你的终极目标是活下来。因此，径直生死决斗并不总是最佳策略。埋伏在草丛中，等待最佳时机偷袭或从高地发起袭击，对未察觉的敌人造成巨大伤害。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/792ac1715af701d0519930258bd78489.poster.avif?t=1713182577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/792ac1715af701d0519930258bd78489.webm?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/792ac1715af701d0519930258bd78489.mp4?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>我们期待你的个性化战略。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拥有强大武器的顶级猎人</h2></strong><br>每次进入竞技场，你都可以从17个独一无二的猎人中进行选择。<br>每名猎人都有独一无二的战斗风格，均是东方剑术和法术大师。试着定制属于自己的猎人，使用数不尽的武器皮肤和表情，在竞技中展示风格。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/5ac5d4d34220042303aa6e1503218e99.poster.avif?t=1713182577\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/5ac5d4d34220042303aa6e1503218e99.webm?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/5ac5d4d34220042303aa6e1503218e99.mp4?t=1713182577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一场胜者为王的致命战斗</h2></strong><br>在这个诡谲的世界生存下来，以此证明自己是顶级猎手。在猎人竞技场，你可以暂时与敌人组队猎杀妖怪boss，竞技随即转变成稀有装备的致命抢夺战。征服猎人竞技场，成为最后活下来的猎人吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1061100/extras/1b363c1edcb884199c3dd4f51dad0793.avif?t=1713182577\" width=800 height=450 /></span>",
